类 NodeHashMapImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.zookeeper.server.NodeHashMapImpl
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    NodeHashMap

    public class NodeHashMapImpl
extends Object
implements NodeHashMap
    a simple wrapper to ConcurrentHashMap that recalculates a digest after each mutation.
